text.autoconfig.gelatin.option.addCustom: Whether or not Jello will add it's included 1822 colors to Minecraft internally.
text.autoconfig.gelatin.option.enableDye: Allow for the dyeing of blocks using any vanilla dye.
Allow for the dyeing of entities using any dye.
Allow for the dyeing of players using any dye.

text.autoconfig.gelatin.option.enableTra: Enables a fix for water within cauldrons just being Opaque rather than translucent.
